# Split Bill App

A simple app to manage and split bills with your friends.  
It allows you to add friends, choose who paid the bill, and calculate who owes whom.  
Built with **React** and organized into reusable components.

---

## ✨ Features
- 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 Add new friends with profile images.
- 💰 Enter the bill amount and specify who paid.
- 🔄 Automatically calculate balances between you and your friends.
- ✅ Clean, simple, Responsive UI design.
- ⚡️ Organized components for scalability.

---

## 📂 Project Structure

src/
│ App.jsx
│ main.jsx
│ index.css
└── components/
   │ Friend.jsx
   │ FriendsList.jsx
   │ Button.jsx
   │ FormAddFriend.jsx
   │ FormSplitBill.jsx


---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **React**: Frontend library for building UI.
- **JavaScript (ES6+)**: Core logic.
- **CSS**: Styling and layout.
- **Crypto UUID**: Generate unique IDs for friends.

